From 41ccadbf1f228b0222f81c8e331086871e6639fb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Eric Fine <efine2010@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 01:55:08 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add auth, Golf/Housewares warehouse tabs, Item Master
 tabs, warehouse summary

- Password protection (session-based auth with httponly cookies)
- Login page with GolfGen branding and Sign Out button in header
- Golf Warehouse tab with channel filter (Amazon/Walmart/Other)
- Housewares Warehouse tab with inventory display
- Item Master now has Amazon/Walmart/Other tabs
- Inventory page shows 3PL warehouse summary (Golf vs Housewares)
- Added JSON data files for warehouse inventory and item masters
- Updated Dockerfile to include new data files
- Rebuilt frontend with all new components

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
